---
title: Easy Cheesy Orzo Risotto with Chorizo, Tomato and Mozzarella
description: We love this recipe because we use orzo - a teeny-tiny rice shaped pasta - to make a faux risotto! By stirring in fresh pearl bocconcini just before serving, there's some cheesy gooey-ness in every bite! Best of all - it's all cooked in one pot!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-cheesy-orzo-risotto-f423f796.jpg
